These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-1::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, snowmobile
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, chaman
2 different games are played: billiard, bridge
House: victorian, futuristic
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, jazz
There are 2 different favourite colors: grey, blue
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, october
1. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
2. the person who likes blue is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
4. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
5. the person who's birthday is in october is the person playing bridge##1
6. the futuristic house is the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Transport      | snowmobile        | train |
| Cigar          | chaman  | baccarat     |
| Game         | bridge    | billiard         |
| House           | victorian    | futuristic |
| Music-Genre   | pop  | jazz     |
| Color           | blue      | grey    |
| Birthday         | october | august          |

