3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the fan of folk##1
5. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |
